{"tid":2222363,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆成日少少野都認叨又踩低阿媽抬高自己","createTime":"2020-09-29T04:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T07:39:13.000Z","uid":134683,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"182154cfa5b721c8b6357dc8cb3a83a23381ff2d","tid":2222363,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:52:13.000Z","msg":"老豆差幾年就80<br />\n份人冇乜野又唔會持老賣老<br />\n都算關心我同兩個孫<br />\n但係就乜都要認叨<br />\n離遠少少睇到巴士號碼、冇乜病痛呢啲都要吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲更係少事<br />\n咪當佢東方昇讚自己碌野大咁笑下就算<br />\n有時識少少就講大道理當自己專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOk咪尤佢吹<br />\n但好多時都講錯哂<br />\n我又唔想對仔女聽錯既知識<br />\n咁就無辦法唔開聲<br />\n但又好似落佢面咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最離譜係有次又係為咗認叨恥笑阿媽<br />\n我忍唔住爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆成世都未大聲鬧過我<br />\n果次佢可能飲大咗<br />\n喊哂咁小老母喊生喊死拮大脾嬲左我幾日<br />\n我估嗰幾日阿媽一定好慘俾佢日鬧夜鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇佢個勢<br />\n越老可能越諗歪一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e9a7bd5f44e77072113a559cfa752756cbde46","tid":2222363,"uid":37085,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:59:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喊哂咁小老母喊生喊死拮大脾嬲左我幾日</blockquote><br />\n睇嚟樓主都有啲言語障礙 唔怪得個老豆覺得自己好醒"},{"pid":"4840dcd63e3673b5da8cc5788065b68875b39eed","tid":2222363,"uid":366156,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T05:10:41.000Z","msg":"好多男人都係咁"},{"pid":"d3c20343c78a996a82cad340ed03979a292a13b4","tid":2222363,"uid":215026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03e9a7bd5f44e77072113a559cfa752756cbde46","tid":2222363,"uid":37085,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:59:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喊哂咁小老母喊生喊死拮大脾嬲左我幾日</blockquote><br />\n睇嚟樓主都有啲言語障礙 唔怪得個老豆覺得自己好醒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T15:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />陣間到樓主喊生喊死拮大脾"},{"pid":"d0e865bf59140362dd8603e51ccae2c9936dd2b9","tid":2222363,"uid":241240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4840dcd63e3673b5da8cc5788065b68875b39eed","tid":2222363,"uid":366156,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T05:10:41.000Z","msg":"好多男人都係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"自大源於無知不限於男女<br />\n但男性瓶鹽令到成件事柒多一個碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申巴"}]}